%% ============================================================
%% DIAGRAM 12: Hive Mind Orchestration Flow
%% ============================================================

---
title: "Hive Mind Orchestration — Multi-Agent Coordination"
---
graph TB
    START([User Request]) --> TRIAGE["HIVE MIND TRIAGE<br/><b>qwen3.5:397b-cloud</b>"]

    TRIAGE -->|DIRECT<br/>"Show pipeline"| DEXEC["DIRECT EXECUTOR<br/>Single tool call"]
    TRIAGE -->|WORKFLOW<br/>"Roleplay call"| COACH["COACH AGENT<br/>Typed subgraph"]
    TRIAGE -->|WORKFLOW<br/>"Research company"| ASSIST["ASSISTANT AGENT<br/>Typed subgraph"]
    TRIAGE -->|COMPLEX<br/>"Prepare for QBR"| PM["PM AGENT<br/>Task decomposition"]

    DEXEC --> RESPOND[Respond to User]
    COACH --> RESPOND
    ASSIST --> RESPOND

    PM --> TASKGRAPH["TaskGraph DAG<br/>Typed tasks + dependencies"]
    TASKGRAPH --> BATCH1["Batch 1: Parallel<br/>Fetch data sources"]
    BATCH1 --> BATCH2["Batch 2: Sequential<br/>Analyze patterns"]
    BATCH2 --> BATCH3["Batch 3: Generate<br/>QBR deck + summary"]

    BATCH3 --> REVIEWER["REVIEWER AGENT<br/>Quality validation"]
    REVIEWER -->|APPROVED| RESPOND
    REVIEWER -->|CHANGES REQUIRED| BATCH3

    subgraph MEMORY["MEMORY SYSTEM (SQLite)"]
        LESSONS["Project Lessons"]
        PREFS["User Preferences"]
        FAILURES["Execution Failures"]
        PATTERNS["Successful Patterns"]
    end

    PM -.->|inject context| MEMORY
    REVIEWER -.->|extract lessons| MEMORY

    style TRIAGE fill:#FF6B35,color:#fff
    style PM fill:#6B5CE7,color:#fff
    style REVIEWER fill:#EF4444,color:#fff
    style MEMORY fill:#1B4332,color:#fff


%% ============================================================
%% DIAGRAM 13: Data Flow — End-to-End for a Coaching Request
%% ============================================================

---
title: "End-to-End Data Flow: Rep Asks for Meeting Prep"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Rep as Sales Rep
    participant Slack as Slack
    participant Bolt as Bolt SDK
    participant Triage as Triage<br/>(qwen3.5:397b-cloud)
    participant Coach as Coach<br/>(qwen3.5:397b-cloud)
    participant RAG as RAG Pipeline<br/>(Voyage + Qdrant)
    participant HS as HubSpot<br/>MCP
    participant Web as Web Search<br/>MCP
    participant BQ as BigQuery<br/>MCP
    participant Mem as Memory<br/>(SQLite)

    Rep->>Slack: /coach prep for QBR with Acme Corp
    Slack->>Bolt: slash_command event
    Bolt->>Triage: Classify complexity

    Triage->>Mem: Inject user preferences
    Mem-->>Triage: User prefers MEDDIC

    Triage-->>Bolt: complexity = WORKFLOW, route = coach

    Bolt->>Coach: Execute prep workflow

    par Parallel data gathering
        Coach->>HS: Get Acme Corp deals, contacts, recent notes
